<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 32pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;">3月26日，江西软件职业技术大学开展了一场热闹非凡的游园赏花活动。2000米长的樱花大道上，汉服踏青、动漫表演、模特队打卡、音乐表演、花海跳舞等丰富的活动融合诗情画意，让万余名师生及游在欣赏春日的美好与浪漫的同时感受校园里学子们的青春风采与蓬勃活力。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 32pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 32pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-03-26%2019%3A34%3A13%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20240326193424.jpg?Expires=2026812853&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=Vx3hCguYAdAei3acFsi9cpAymoA%3D" alt="" width="650" height="482" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; v